data.description:
Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single level home located on the west side of Ennis, a couple of blocks from the post office! The open layout of the kitchen and living room make entertaining easy! Large fenced in back yard with an irrigation system for your pets! 2 stall attached garage, as well as a 3rd garage (16X24) accessed in the alley! An hour from Yellowstone National Park An hour from Bozeman Yellowstone National Airport. 
Now offering seller financing wth agreeable terms! 

Call the listing agent or your preferred realtor to set up your showing today!
